org.kitteh.irc.client.library.feature.sts

Class MemoryStsMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kitteh.irc.client.library.feature.sts.MemoryStsMachine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StsMachine

    public class MemoryStsMachine
extends Object
implements StsMachine
    "Memory" prefix to distinguish implementation class from interface, because StsMachine isn't IStsMachine. This class implements our FSM in an in-memory fashion, using Java's data structures.
